5:
I am very grateful for your help,
everyone. Let's make this concert a
great one.
9:
No need to be so formal, Junko.
We're assistants, that's what we're
here to do!
16:
I'm just expressing gratitude for your
help in setting up the concert.
Without you, it simply couldn't have
been done.
20:
You really are quite mature for your
age, aren't you!
23:
Number 4! Rehearsal is starting
soon, if you don't mind!
30:
If I could just see your ticket, please.
Yes, you're good to go!
38:
U-uh, I don't know what you're
talking about! Maybe you've got the
wrong person!
47:
What's the matter? Are you also
going to feature in the concert?
51:
Actually... I came to watch Junko
perform.
52:
I still have a lot to learn when it
comes to being an idol... Also, I
wanted to see the show from a fan's
perspective.
57:
I see. I guess we should keep this a
secret from Junko?
69:
Thank you so much for coming to
my solo performance today!
71:
Tell me, have some of you been to a
concert before?
74:
I see! I'm thrilled that you chose my
concert as your first one.
81:
Wow, this is totally different from her
usual vibe.
89:
Even when performing alone, she
doesn't fail to impress. I always see
her from up close, but this is quite
different...
95:
Ai-san, you could have told me that
you planned on coming to my
concert.
99:
I was worried that if I told you, you'd
put on a different performance than
you normally would. I wanted to see
the real you.
101:
You're definitely a tough one, Junko.
That much was obvious just
watching you perform!
107:
I felt like I was watching an entirely
different person!
111:
Yes, you were much more imposing
and grand than usual.
115: You were dazzling. And really cool.
119: Thank you very much for saying that.
122:
What'd you think of Number 4's
concert today?
123:
Yeah, she's a pro. No weak spots in
her performance whatsoever.
126:
Curious what the fans are talking
about? Why don't we have a seat
over there.
128:
If we sit far enough away, nobody
will think twice about what we're
doing.
136:
Yeah, Number 4's voice is pretty
sweet. The cuteness factor really
adds to her voice. Real groovy.
138:
And the fact that she never runs out
of breath is just unbelievable. The
lungs on that girl! I just wish that she
was a bit more exciting, you know?
140:
I see what you mean, if you
compare her to Number 2's
rough-and-tumble style, or Number
6's crowd-pleasing antics... I
suppose she's a bit lacking in
impact?
142: I definitely like Number 6 the most!
144:
Nah, I think Number 5 is where it's at.
She's got a spontaneity to her... Plus
she's way more mature!
146:
Oh you guys are definitely idol
amateurs. There's no doubt that
Number 1 is the greatest of them all!
Number 3 is pretty good too, all
things considered.
149:
Everyone has their own opinion!
Don't pay them any attention!
152:
Yeah, it really does all come down to
personal preference...
167: (Perhaps I need to relax a bit...)
169:
(If I shut myself in, I might start
growing mushrooms again...)
179:
I must be tired if I'm hallucinating
talking mushrooms now. I better go
for a walk...
184:
Alk, Stella? What are you two doing
here?
188: We came to see you, Junko.
193:
Stella insisted that we come. Felt it
would be a good change of pace.
199:
Um, I was wondering if you would be
able to take me to another world? I
feel that would make for a good
refresher right about now.
207:
Thank you so much. I'll just need to
get a few things in order. Please wait
for me.
211:
I am Junko Konno, the Showa Idol...
There's nothing that worries me. Not
a thing.
